Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Bolinas Ridge
Description: A scenic overlook which I visited often when I lived at home.

Name: Steep Ravine Ladder
Description: This ladder is on my favorite hiking trail and is one of the most unique features I've seen on a trail.

Name: Inspiration Point
Description: This point is one of the most satisfying panoramic views I've ever gazed upon, with views spanning across all of Santa Barbara.

Name: Twin Peaks
Description: The view I cherish the most of the city I was born in: San Francisco.

Name: Flight Deck
Description: When I was younger I had an obsession with this rollercoaster and is one of my favorite locations to this day.
